{"tid":2015744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歌唱家激似習近平 抖音賬號被封","createTime":"2020-05-14T02:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T02:08:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57e9f882ede7f7865d6d73fa0b8eddc9924d1d03","tid":2015744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200514/PCMCTM4YN4RE7CGI34MOFFAAPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200514%2FPCMCTM4YN4RE7CGI34MOFFAAPQ%2F&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=0476fe69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200514%2FPCMCTM4YN4RE7CGI34MOFFAAPQ%2F&h=f4bb0ffc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200514/PCMCTM4YN4RE7CGI34MOFFAAPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n歌唱家激似習近平 抖音賬號被封<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旅居歐洲的中國著名演唱家劉克清疑因和中國國家主席習近平「撞臉」，在內地短片分享平台抖音被指「形象違規」遭遇封號，他後來更換頭像造型照片，賬號才獲解封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200514/large/1589386636_0f30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200514%2Flarge%2F1589386636_0f30.jpg&h=17d73f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉克清與習近平「撞臉」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屢被投訴頭像違規<br />\n<br />\n現年63歲的劉克清目前人在德國，他去年九月開設抖音賬號，發放聲樂教學影片，瞬間獲得逾37萬人次按讚。網絡照。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。有人以為他冒充習近平：「可能是誤會，有些人看到照片以為是，以為我冒充，我自己本身不覺得甚麼，他們覺得挺像的，可能有不太好影響，所以他們（抖音）向我提出了認證。」他隨後將頭像換成演出時的造型照，事件大致解決，抖音賬號也恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n劉身邊不少朋友也認為，他極像習近平：「我自己沒有甚麼感覺，但就是很多人說，譬如跟朋友聚會，他們就說：『怎麼你那麼像？』差不多有兩年多以來，很多人。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"2b10be2569e0e23dbe42ef9b8e9708717623a119","tid":2015744,"uid":274316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3x3Y8je.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3x3Y8je.jpg&h=28d81a22&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}